<body>
<h1>Input your stock holdings to find an appropriate ETF(s) to replace them with</h1>
<div class="col-lg-4">
    <h4 class="card-title">Input Instructions</h4>
    <h6 class="card-subtitle">Input one row for each of the stock holding</h6>
    <ul class="list-icons">
        <li><a href="javascript:void(0)"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>First text box: Stock Name</a></li>
        <li><a href="javascript:void(0)"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>Second text box: Market Value of your
                holding (number of shares you own * today's market price of the stock)</a></li>
    </ul>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-4">
    <h4 class="card-title">FAQs</h4>
    <h6 class="card-subtitle">With that information, we will look for potential ETFs for you to replace, or consolidate
        your holdings into.</h6>
    <ul class="list-icons">
        <li><a href="javascript:void(0)"><i class="fa fa-check text-info"></i>Do we record your data? Answer: <b>No</b></a>
        </li>
        <li><a href="javascript:void(0)"><i class="fa fa-check text-info"></i>Do we send your data across the wire?
                Answer: Yes, but only to our backend servers for processing. But you don't
                need to just take our word! We've open sourced our backend <a href="">here</a>. So please feel free to
                verify!</a></li>
        <li><a href="javascript:void(0)"><i class="fa fa-check text-info"></i>Do we record your data? Answer: <b>No</b></a>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>

<section id="holdings-content">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <form action="/find_overlaps.html" method="post" id="frm_data">
                        <table class="table table-striped table table-bordered">
                            <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Sl.</th>
                                <th>Stock Name</th>
                                <th>Market Value in USD</th>
                                <th><input type="button" value="+" id="addnew" title="Click to Add New Row"/></th>
                            </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody id="tbl_body">
                            <tr>
                                <td>1</td>
                                <td><label>
                                        <input type="text" name="stocks[1]" placeholder="AAPL"/>
                                    </label></td>
                                <td><label>
                                        <input type="number" name="market_values[1]" placeholder="10,000"/>
                                    </label></td>
                                <td title="This Row Can't be Deleted"></td>
                            </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                        <span class="input-group-btn">
                        <input style="margin-top: 20px" type="submit" value="Find me ETFs!" id="sub_button"
                               title="Save the Record" class="btn btn-primary btn-group-right"/>
                        </span>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

